Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鳥のさえずり）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（室戸(むろと) 菫(すみれ)のあくび）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:09.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sensei, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（里見(さとみ)蓮太郎(れんたろう)）\N先生 聞いてんのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:14.91,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was thinking about what \Nto make for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ すまん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今晩のおかず\N何 作ろうか考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話してみろって言うから\N相談したんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.84,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I was telling you about this \Nbecause you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:23.30,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,The discrimination against the \NCursed Children in the Tokyo Area...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリアに はびこる\N呪われた子供たちへの差別…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:28.09,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,And your concerns about how your lives are \Ngoing to be, now that Enju-chan's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 昨日 延珠(えんじゅ)ちゃんの出自が\N学校にバレたことによる―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:30.50,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,has been revealed at her school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今後の生活への不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.01,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Your problems are so normal, \Nthey're rather boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の悩みは あまりに普通すぎて\Nつまらんのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてんじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）そもそも\N人類は どうして―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:42.07,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Why does humanity have to \Nexterminate Gastrea, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアを\Nせん滅しなければならない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:44.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Because it's the enemy of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人類の敵だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.40,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,But there are religious sects that \Nbelieve Gastrea is a messenger of God
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界では ガストレアを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地球を浄化するために現れた\N神の使いだと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:52.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神聖視している宗教団体もある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.15,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,that has come to cleanse the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:56.28,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,As they see it, humanity is responsible for using up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らに言わせれば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人類こそが 資源を食い尽くして\N地球をダメにする要因だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.99,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,all the world's resources, and destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.17,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's just an extreme point of view\Nregarding humanity as unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 最終的に\N人類は不要だっていう極論だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Besides, if Gastrea is a messenger of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも\Nガストレアが神の使いなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:07.46,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,what does that make the Cursed Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪われた子供たちは\Nなんだっていうんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:13.84,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Agents of God serving as messengers \Nbetween humanity and Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人類とガストレアとの\Nメッセンジャーを務める―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju is a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠は人間だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She is a human being with \Na personality and a will!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つの人格と意志をそなえた\N人間だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して それ以上でも\Nそれ以下でもねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She is nothing more and nothing less!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:25.77,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Exactly. See? You do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおり 分かってるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:29.61,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Listen, Rentaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）なあ 蓮太郎くん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:34.33,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,At least you know who you are \Nand where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 自分がどこの誰か\N知っているだけ まだいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.73,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Enju-chan doesn't even \Nknow that about herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠ちゃんは\Nそれすらも知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:41.49,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Most of the Cursed Children in the \Nouter district were abandoned children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外周区の呪われた子供たちは\Nほとんど捨て子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.50,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,They never know their parents \Nor anything of the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:45.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女たちは 親も外の世界も\N知らないまま―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.99,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,and are only viewed with scorn by most.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多くの人間から\N軽蔑のまなざしで見られる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:54.98,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,So who's going support, \Nteach, and lead those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな彼女たちを支え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:54.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教え導いてやれるのは 誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君たちは 家族じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.37,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Aren't you two family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生 ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:11.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）あっ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:11.98,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.71,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,I've got a message from your patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君のパトロンから伝言だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.83,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,He says to visit the student \Ncouncil office once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまには 生徒会室に\N遊びに来いとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:22.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.52,Bullet_Main,teach,0,0,0,,Is this Satomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（担任）里見さんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.17,Bullet_Main,teach,0,0,0,,I'm Aihara-san's homeroom teacher. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（担任）藍原(あいはら)さんの担任です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.78,Bullet_Main,teach,0,0,0,,Aihara-san came to school this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,藍原さんが\N今朝から登校してまして…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）すぐ 行きます！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:43.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.80,Bullet_Ep_Title,ep,0,0,0,,{\fad(425,465)}#03 The Children of Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:11.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（少年）学校 来んなよ！\N（少女）ダマしてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.15,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,Stop coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.15,Bullet_Main,kid,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.98,Bullet_Main,girl,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（少女）そばに来ないで！\N（少年）帰れよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:17.98,Bullet_Main,boy,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.61,Bullet_Main,boy,0,0,0,,You stupid Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（少年）ガストレアめ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.57,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you guys killing anyone \Nand everyone, my family was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが 所構わず\N殺しまくったせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺んちは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.24,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,That wasn't me! I am human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（藍原延珠）それは 妾(わらわ)じゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾は人間だ！ あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.04,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾は…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 妾は…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.45,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I am... human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.75,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.80,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,let's change schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校を移ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:53.24,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I do not... want to... give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾は…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたく… ない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:57.31,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I made... so many friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達も たくさんできたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,They aren't your friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 友達じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.28,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:09.69,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Even so, do we still have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも 妾たちは\N戦わなければならないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヘリのローター音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:22.06,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun! We've located the Gastrea \Nthat was the source of infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童(てんどう)木更(きさら)）里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感染源ガストレアの潜伏先が\N分かったわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.34,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,We're going to get there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うちが一番乗りよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.81,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Did you really have to call Dr. Heli?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって ドクターヘリを…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.21,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,I used up next year's tuition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）来年分の学費\N使い込んじゃったから―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.85,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,so if anyone beats us to it, \NI'll have to quit school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よそに取られたら\N私 中退よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.82,Bullet_Main,pilot,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは なんでしょうか？\N（蓮太郎）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's a Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There are spiders that use webs \Nas parachutes and travel around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巣をパラシュート状に編んで\N旅をするクモがいるが―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.74,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと似たような原理で…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.32,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか これが\N先生の言っていた―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.70,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,This is one of the original abilities \Nthat Sensei was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリジナルの能力ってやつか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（後部ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て 延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアの悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ… 高度を下げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Decrease altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.17,Bullet_Main,pilot,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（操縦士）えっ？\N（蓮太郎）早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.26,Bullet_Main,pilot,0,0,0,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:29.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアの悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.18,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro... I defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 倒したぞ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.46,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I have defeated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾が倒したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.87,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ 妾は戦っただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I fought it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.98,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I protected... everyone in school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校のみんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.56,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:15.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠の泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:17.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It may be true that all we \Ncan do right now is fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）確かに 今は\N戦うしかないかもしれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And I know how anxious you feel, \Nbeing unsure which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに向かえばいいか―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安に思う気持ちも分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.61,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,But, Enju, you have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠 お前には俺がいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I care about you more than anyone else does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を大切に思う気持ちは\N誰にも負けねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Even if the world doesn't accept you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしも 世界が\Nお前を受け入れなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.68,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll always be right by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は いつでも\Nお前のそばにいる！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.77,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう 蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.10,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All right. Let's get what we \Ncame here for and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ とっとと回収して\Nうちに帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.44,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I wonder what's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:57.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）何が入ってんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The Inheritance of the Seven Stars, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,七星の遺産か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.83,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤな予感がする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.96,Bullet_Main,samon,0,0,0,,Well done, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子(ひるこ)影胤(かげたね)）\Nご苦労だったね 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うわっ！ うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.97,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！ あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.44,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Found you, Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子小比奈(こひな)）延珠 見ーつけた\N（延珠）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.81,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts First Style, Number 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式戦闘術 一の型八番！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.52,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Homura Kasen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焔火扇(ほむらかせん)！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ううっ\N（影胤）フフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）\N（蓮太郎）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:35.49,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I'll show you a move of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:35.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）１つ 君に\N私の技を見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.35,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Maximum Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マキシマムペイン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（指を鳴らす音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.51,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Oh? You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\Nほう まだ生きているか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.47,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju... Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠 逃げろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… イヤだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.30,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.27,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.09,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Wait right there, Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってろ 蓮太郎ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.70,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa! Enju ran away! I want to cut her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ！ 延珠 逃げた！\N斬りたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.87,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,No, daughter of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ダメだよ 我が娘よ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.89,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,If they join with other civil \Nofficers, it'll be a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの民警と合流されたら\N面倒なことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.46,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Let us finish our job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕事を済ませよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刀を刺す音）\Nうっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:35.30,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,You're so weak... You're so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱いくせに！ 弱いくせに！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:47.11,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Any final words, my dying friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）何か言い残すことは？\N死にゆく友よ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄に…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.78,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,to hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.19,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）グッドナイト
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.69,Bullet_Flashback,doc,0,0,0,,You are Satomi Rentaro-kun, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菫）里見蓮太郎くんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.10,Bullet_Flashback,doc,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじめまして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.71,Bullet_Flashback,doc,0,0,0,,There's a choice I'd like you to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に 選んでほしいことがあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Oh, Kisara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 木更さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.26,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）おかえりなさい 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.61,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,How long have I been asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 どのくらい寝てた？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.33,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,One day and about three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）丸１日と３時間くらい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.54,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,They said your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:44.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の心臓 手術の最後の最後で\N動きだしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.53,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,started beating toward the \Nvery end of the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.49,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,You didn't give up on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きることを諦めなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.37,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:48.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偉いわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.75,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The government has given us some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政府側から 情報が伝えられたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.90,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The case that Kagetane took contains
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影胤が持ち去った ケースの中身は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.63,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,a catalyst capable of \Nsummoning a Stage Five Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアのステージⅤを\N呼び出すことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触媒だそうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Stage Five?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.14,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,You mean, of the eleven that \Nalmost destroyed the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それって 世界を滅ぼした11体の？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.35,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Starting from Stage One,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅠから始まり\NⅡ Ⅲと成長し―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.41,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Gastrea grows to Stage Two and Three, \Nthen completes itself at Stage Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ⅳで完成するガストレア
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.65,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The Stage Fives exist outside of that evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その進化の枠外に存在する\NステージⅤ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:18.09,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,They've existed since the \Nappearance of Gastrea ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前の\Nガストレア誕生時からいて―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.18,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,They're larger than other Gastrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どのガストレアより巨大で―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.66,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,and Varanium magnetic fields \Nhave no effect on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バラニウムの磁場に\N一切 影響を受けない存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.10,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Monoliths have been destroyed in various areas
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤによって―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくつかのエリアで\Nモノリスが壊されたことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.10,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,by these Stage Fives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:34.18,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,And the hordes of Gastrea that \Ninfiltrate afterwards bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雪崩を打って侵入してくる―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかのガストレアたちが\N引き起こすものは―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.52,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大絶滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:42.08,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Hiruko Kagetane has escaped the Monolith \Nbarrier into the Unexplored Territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛭子影胤は\N今 モノリスの外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未踏査領域に逃げ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.89,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,and has begun preparations \Nfor summoning the Stage Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤを呼び寄せる準備に\N入っている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:50.02,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The government is about to launch \Nan extensive pursuit operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:50.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まもなく 政府主導で\N大々的な追撃作戦が発動されるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And if that doesn't stop them, \Nthe Tokyo Area will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで ヤツらを止められなければ\N東京エリアは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.93,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,You're planning to go? Can you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行く気なの？ 勝てるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.44,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てなきゃ ダメなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:00.69,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,You're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:02.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟のうえだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.03,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be resting, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）\N君 絶対安静なのよ 本当は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kisara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い 木更さん 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.12,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.50,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,There's someone else you should \Nbe apologizing to before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の前に 謝る相手がいるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 延珠!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:21.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:22.88,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シーッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,When did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）いつの間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:27.50,Bullet_Main,kisra,0,0,0,,Ever since you were brought in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）あなたが\Nここに運び込まれてから ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.39,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro... you imbecile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 アホ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:37.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Man... I really am useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 ホント ダメダメだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:40.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I made you worry, Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配かけたな 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.15,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.16,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.85,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）あなたによ\N（蓮太郎）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.29,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It's Seitenshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）聖天子(せいてんし)様から\N（蓮太郎）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:59.70,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san, we will be initiating an \Noperation to pursue Hiruko Kagetane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）里見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛭子影胤 追撃作戦が始まります
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.17,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,I would like you to participate in this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は あなたに この作戦に\N参加してほしいと思っています
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.16,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）どうして 俺なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.18,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,You should know that better than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）それは―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが一番\N分かっているはずですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.78,Bullet_Flashback,,0,0,0,,Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.70,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,Just remember that I'm not doing this for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あんたらのために\Nやるわけじゃないことを―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れんな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.99,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,I wish you luck, Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）ご武運を 里見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.20,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,From your patron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君のパトロンからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.92,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,Thank him with the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,礼は 手柄をあげて返してやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.23,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,This is a farewell gift from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 私からのせん別だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.20,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,AGV experimental drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＡＧＶ試験薬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.96,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,If you can avoid it, don't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できれば 使うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:43.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,While I was unconscious, I had a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意識がなくなってるときにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.59,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,of when you operated on me ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前 先生に\N執刀される夢を見たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:54.60,Bullet_Main,doc,0,0,0,,What I did to you can never be \Nforgiven, no matter what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が君にやったことは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:55.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな言葉を尽くしても\N許されることではないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:04.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I've never once resented you since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は あの日から
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度だって 先生のことを\N恨んだことなんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.91,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,I order you as the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,社長として命令します
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.37,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Crush the Kagetane and Kohina pair and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影胤 小比奈ペアを撃破して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.63,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,stop them from summoning the Stage Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤ召喚を止めなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:20.92,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Give me a hundred times more \Neffort than you have in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は 私のために\N今までの100倍 働いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.67,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,and I'll give you a thousand times back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 君の1000倍働くから！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.92,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I will stop them, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 止めてみせます\Nあなたのためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,For your sake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（物音）\N（延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… 危ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爆発音）\N（２人）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:55.03,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it! Some pair is using explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかのペアが\N爆発物を使ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.48,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは なんだ？\N（蓮太郎）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A Stage Four?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅣ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:16.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠･蓮太郎）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うりゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ハァ… 延珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒヒッ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動くな！ あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.42,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Wait! Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て 延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She's not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）あ…\N（蓮太郎）こいつは敵じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:18.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 俺のことを覚えてるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.92,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（千寿(せんじゅ)夏世(かよ)）もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）待て待て\N妾は こんな女 知らないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I do not know this woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.40,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Explain what this is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう関係か説明しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:32.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She's the partner of a Promoter named \NIkuma Shogen. She's an Initiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nこいつは 伊熊将監(いくましょうげん)っていう―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:33.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プロモーターの相棒\Nイニシエーターだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.65,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm Senju Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千寿夏世です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.29,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじめまして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:39.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）フンッ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.66,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I will not accept such a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾は あんな女 認めないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:44.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I only asked her to keep watch outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外で見張りしてろって\N言っただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.84,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Why did she get so moody?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで あんな不機嫌になんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.53,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I believe the reason is clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理由は 明白なように思えますが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.29,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Am I strange to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不思議ですか？ 私が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.59,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… いや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.23,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm an Initiator with the model of a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は イルカの因子を持つ\Nイニシエーター
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:04.02,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I just have a higher IQ and \Nbetter memory than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常より 知能指数と\N記憶能力が高いだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You're the smart one, \Nyet you're the rear guard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\N頭脳派のお前が後衛で―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.07,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and Shogen is the vanguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将監が前衛なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's a pretty unusual style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,珍しいスタイルだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.52,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Shogen-san is all muscle, \Nright down to his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）将監さんは脳みそまで\N筋肉で出来ているうえ―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:16.53,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,On top of that, he's just \Ntoo stingy to do backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バックアップなんて\Nみみっちいことが―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できないだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Let me see your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の銃 見せてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.99,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,What if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤだと言ったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:25.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's fine, if you feel \Nnothing about being saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かまわねえぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が助けられたことを\N何も感じてないならな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.40,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I have learned one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ 学びました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:34.05,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Once you expect something in \Nreturn, your good deed fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:34.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見返りを求めた時点で\N善行は堕落しますね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why did you use explosives in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 森で爆発物を使った？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:40.52,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,A trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワナに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:44.59,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,We could see a pattern of \Nflashing lights deep in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,森の奥で点滅する\Nライトパターンが見えましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.94,Bullet_Main,senju,0,0,0,,We thought they were fellow \Ncivil officers and went closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,民警だと思って\N近づいていったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And it was a Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nそれが ガストレアだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.27,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Without thinking, I used a high-explosive shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっさに 榴弾(りゅうだん)を\N使ってしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.71,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,And then we were attacked by \Nthe Gastrea in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで 森のガストレアに襲われて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.45,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and I was separated from Shogen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将監さんと\Nはぐれてしまっているわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Did the Gastrea inject any fluid into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ガストレアに\N体液を注入されたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.42,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,The fluid it injected was a very small amount,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,注入された体液は\Nごく少量でしたので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.71,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,so there is no increase in the corrosion rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,侵食率の上昇はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.21,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,There is no need to worry about \Nme turning into a Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が ガストレア化する心配は\Nありませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Listen. Make sure you get \Nchecked out once we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか？ 戻ったら\Nちゃんと検査しておけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.59,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,You are worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私を心配しているんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）悪いか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.22,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm a little envious of Enju-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 少しだけ\N延珠さんが羨ましいです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:31.83,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,She has never killed anyone before, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠さんは おそらく\N人を殺したことがありませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.49,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I can tell by looking at her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目を見れば 分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）お前は あんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:39.70,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Indeed. Even on our way here, \NI killed another pair that we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）ええ\Nここに来る途中も―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出会ったペアを殺しました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして そんなことを？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.03,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Because Shogen-san ordered me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）将監さんの命令です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.64,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn't let anyone have the reward
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮面野郎をぶち殺す手柄は\N誰にも渡さないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.37,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,for killing the guy in the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.27,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I was scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖かったです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.04,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,My hands shook, but that was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手が震えました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.59,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I believe I'll get used to it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じき慣れると思います
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't give me that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ふざけんじゃねえ！\N（夏世）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:02.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The scariest thing about killing \Npeople is getting used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺人の一番怖いところは\N慣れることだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,When you kill someone and realize \Nyou won't be punished...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人を殺し 自分が\N罰せられないと知ったとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.96,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's when people forget \Nall about punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は 罪の意識を忘れていく！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.65,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Are you able to say that because \Nyou've killed someone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは あなたが\N人を殺したことがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言えるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:17.25,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,You have very mysterious eyes, Satomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）里見さんは\N不思議な瞳をしていますね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.90,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have a complicated past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと 複雑な過去を\Nお持ちなのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.91,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,You're so kind, yet you \Nhave such a scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優しいのに… とても怖い顔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why am I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.41,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,trying to talk like I know everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 偉そうなこと言ってんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sorry about that... \NForget what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い　今の忘れてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.67,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）あっ\N（夏世）どうして 謝るんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.32,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,What you're saying is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さんの言っていることは\N正しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.94,Bullet_Main,senju,0,0,0,,You are right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは正しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.92,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,There's... something wrong with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私… 今 変です
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:49.35,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I can immediately come up with various \Narguments to what you just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さんに対する反論なら\N即座に何十個も思いつくのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.69,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,and yet I don't want to deny your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さんの言ってくれたこと\N否定したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:57.20,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I've never... felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この気持ち…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.53,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（無線のノイズ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.25,Bullet_Italics,shogen,0,0,0,,Hey! If you're alive, reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊熊将監）おい！\N生きてんだったら返事しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.09,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe, Shogen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご無事で何よりです 将監さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.92,Bullet_Italics,shogen,0,0,0,,Kayo, I have great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（将監）夏世 いいニュースがある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.62,Bullet_Italics,shogen,0,0,0,,I found the bastard in the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮面野郎を見つけたぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So you're really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）やっぱり 行くのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.76,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Despite how he is, he is my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）あんな人でも\N私のパートナーなので
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:22.42,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,What about you, Satomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Other than you two, there are \Nten pairs attacking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）将監以外に\N10組以上のペアが―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めてるんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:28.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'll at least see how the fight ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いの結末だけでも 見届けるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.90,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Do you know what that is, Satomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さん\Nあれが何か ご存じですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The Stairway to Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）天(あま)の梯子(はしご)か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.98,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,It is an example of a mass murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）殺りく兵器の代表です
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.90,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,A symbol of the Stolen Generation's hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“奪われた世代”の憎悪の象徴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.41,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,The current generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の時代は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:47.99,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Is what's going on right now really \Na wholesome attempt at revival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 行われているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:49.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に 健全な\N復興なんでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,That's where Kagetane is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこに 影胤が…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:29.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:39.98,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,#04 Black Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.30,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro...
